metadata.description:
Cheugy AI is a truly unique NFT collection of AI-generated images that represent all things we consider to be cheugy. 

Prompted by social commentary from Twitter, TikTok, and Instagram via a PAGER. Created with DeepAI text to image generator. Hand-selected and curated by humans. 

This first collection that mixes the old school ways of connecting via pagers and flip phones, with the twist of modern day Artificial Intelligence technology. Follow us on TikTok, Instagram, and Twitter!

https://www.twitter.com/CheugyAI

https://www.tiktok.com/@cheugyai

https://www.instagram.com/cheugyai
metadata.name: Cheugy NFT #1
